<p>Dave starts off today&rsquo;s show talking about how he&rsquo;s been using his iPhone more and more for turn-by-turn directions, and discusses his picks for the best apps to get the job done. Then he and John discuss the differences between logging out and restarting, a little more about backing up your iDevices, some quirks with Time Machine, and much, much more. Subscribe, download and listen (it&rsquo;s free!), and even feel free to submit a question of your own to John and Dave for a future episode!</p>
